9afe5d24ffa8d1f0a68a","tid":593394,"uid":26030,"like":47,"dislike":5,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T03:26:56.000Z","msg":"其實到底知唔知點解霍金無得拎諾貝爾獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T03:28:34.000Z","msg":"內文解釋得好清楚"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T03:36:16.000Z","msg":"愛因斯坦都無因為相對論得到諾獎<br />\n相對論一定好廢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T04:16:23.000Z","msg":"佢個內文咪話霍金唔夠level拎獎<br />\n根本個原因都唔係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52717694d7812194c545633a2e3274c93a04e9d6","tid":593394,"uid":26030,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"c7b83fe7a3fa29ea6e8d40fe9d104da01d143d61","tid":593394,"uid":26030,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"739709f86eef916123ecbd611d83de624418bdb8","tid":593394,"uid":49359,"like":190,"dislike":9,"score":181,"quote":{"pid":"31e30ff989c19e17bb34cafcf739732d4f4c8aaa","tid":593394,"uid":157439,"like":43,"dislike":5,"score":38,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T03:28:34.000Z","msg":"內文解釋得好清楚"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T03:36:16.000Z","msg":"愛因斯坦都無因為相對論得到諾獎<br />\n相對論一定好廢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T04:16:23.000Z","msg":"佢個內文咪話霍金唔夠level拎獎<br />\n根本個原因都唔係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T04:18:29.000Z","msg":"利申tldr<br />\n只係睇左high light 部份"},{"pid":"c933a69145f5feb3162e1f350830f92af21a4ddf","tid":593394,"uid":157439,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T04:41:29.000Z","msg":"你肯定會問第四個問題了：為什麼霍金輻射沒有得諾貝爾獎？<br />\n<br />\n　　回答是：這只是個理論預測，還沒有被實驗驗證。諾貝爾獎的評選非常慎重，一定要選那些經過驗證、得到公認的成果。這就是為什麼屠呦呦要在發現青蒿素幾十年後才得獎，因為要等到青蒿素大規模使用、成為世界首選的抗瘧疾特效藥之後。即使這麼慎重，還不時有發錯的，諾貝爾獎委員會也是壓力山大。<br />\n<br />\n　　實際上，不要說霍金輻射這樣的對黑洞理論的修正了，就連黑洞本身的存在，還沒有直接的實驗證據呢！當然，絕大多數科學家都相信黑洞的存在，因為間接的證據已經很多了。這種情況就像引力波，在2015年首次直接探測到引力波以前，大多數科學家早就相信了引力波的存在，因為間接的證據已經很充分了。"},{"pid":"c8d061826b68250b59d8ba4794177bd197771c46","tid":593394,"uid":57705,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T04:54:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1d724ee34a2d7af51cc482d4bf8896d128c5590e","tid":593394,"uid":6752,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T05:03:47.000Z","msg":"Higgs boson用左幾多年先驗證到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3538befaa7e8bd551828f1683706c096ed2a1f45","tid":593394,"uid":12475,"like":72,"dislike":5,"score":67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T05:19:06.000Z","msg":"無睇哂既人到底點解可以厚顏無恥地話鳩人？"},{"pid":"7e94d472e633a84ec86398409d77ee1aa94660df","tid":593394,"uid":56185,"like":72,"dislike":0,"score":72,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T05:25:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 霍金啲理論有排都實證唔到 你叫佢點拎諾貝爾獎"},{"pid":"6799d282bbe894bbd0395a908f054bb462bea4a7","tid":593394,"uid":55552,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T05:30:20.000Z","msg":"講學術成就霍金確實唔係楊振寧嗰皮，但話佢拎唔到諾貝爾獎嘅原因係唔夠料就搞錯晒諾貝爾獎嘅評價標準囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9f58c6dc8d4758895f909956e692058f3730e93","tid":593394,"uid":126083,"like":57,"dislike":3,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T05:39:38.000Z","msg":"咪係 的確好多科學家都好難好似楊振寧愛因斯坦咁去提出新框架，但個作者係到咁講科學都要分高層次低層次，足以證明呢個作者都好低層次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab97b3a3af8ff2394e6cb3877969940e3a4cdfae","tid":593394,"uid":37661,"like":53,"dislike":3,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T05:42:22.000Z","msg":"中國科學技術大學化學博士<br />\n<br />\n能創造頭髮豉油、一滴香、地溝油<br />\n<br />\n中國科學家更值得拎諾貝爾獎。"},{"pid":"6b1b19df0f047563d78e1bedf01c7150625d853c","tid":593394,"uid":51559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T05:42:32.000Z","msg":"有生之年都唔知見唔見證到佢啲理論成功實證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7cf235286668f3e4641a5c3c0206b06d6e6d372","tid":593394,"uid":35045,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T05:44:44.000Z","msg":"pH=0<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97bdf32ead290dcc851f27fbfdef8416cfd60970","tid":593394,"uid":43009,"like":21,"dislike":3,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T05:46:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote> 在身體如此極端的禁錮之下，霍金的心靈卻是如此的自由，一直關心著整個宇宙的基本問題，這是多麼感人的英雄形象！《哈姆雷特》里有一句台詞：&ldquo;即使把我關在一個果殼里，我也會把自己當作一個擁有著無限空間的君王。&rdquo;這種精神，在霍金身上正得到了充分的體現。事實上，霍金在《時間簡史》之後，還寫了一部科普著作，就叫做《<span style=\"color: red;\">果殼中的宇宙</span>》。</blockquote><br />\nxxxx in a nutshell意思唔係應該係將好複雜嘅野淺白咁講咩？同佢之前講哈姆雷特嗰種崇高人格唔啦梗喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1691012966e0299d44b0e2f9ea7807713581a220","tid":593394,"uid":125479,"like":11,"dislike":8,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T05:48:21.000Z","msg":"上面啲文科仔係咪睇唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dae5ac22465a21a1fb31d27a00d7496734a8e1c1","tid":593394,"uid":35746,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T05:48:36.000Z","msg":"朗拿度冇囉過歐聯啦<br />\n咁佢係咪垃圾呀"},{"pid":"6b73326f18593cbcdbdcf8be57a00c20f584326b","tid":593394,"uid":161462,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"1691012966e0299d44b0e2f9ea7807713581a220","tid":593394,"uid":125479,"like":11,"dislike":8,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T05:48:21.000Z","msg":"上面啲文科仔係咪睇唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T05:49:29.000Z","msg":"你咁都有得打飛機呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fffe51eebbbdadec14f99ab18e496f9174cf8ccc","tid":593394,"uid":46356,"li